    %a{:href => "https://www.google.com/search?hl=en&q=fake+escrow"}> fake escrow
    " or "
    %a{:href => "https://www.google.com/search?hl=en&q=escrow+fraud"}> escrow fraud
    \."
%p
  %strong
    6.
    %em Distant seller
    asks for a partial payment upfront, after which they will
    %em ship
    goods:
%ul
  %li He says he trusts you with the partial payment.
  %li He may say he has already shipped the goods.
  %li
    Deal often
