      %em sounds too good to be true
%p
  %strong
    7.
    %em Foreign company
    offers you a job receiving payments from customers, then
    %em wiring funds
  %strong :
%ul
  %li Foreign company may claim it is unable to receive payments from its customers directly.
  %li You are typically offered a percentage of payments received.
  %li This kind of "position" may be posted as a job, or offered to you via email.
